% The section name is built in \ttl@a.
% The format is stored in a macro named \ttlf@<section>,
% or \ttlf@<section>/<page> if there is the page spec,
% or \ttlf@.../* if numberless is true
% whose content is
%  \ttl@<shape>{format}{label}{sep}{before}{after}

